  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ArticleDao
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working Article objects with a database.
    CategoryDao
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working Category objects with a database.
    CompanyDao
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working Company objects with a database.
    ContentDao<T extends Content<E>,E extends java.lang.Number>
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working objects of the Content class or subclasses with a database.
    DataDao<T extends Model<E>,E extends java.lang.Number>
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working models objects of the Model class or subclasses with the database.
    FileDao
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working File objects with a database.
    MessageDao
    The class implements a set of standard methods for working models objects of the Message class with the Cache.
    ResponseDao
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working Response objects with a database.
    UserDao
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for working User objects with a database.
